# Tip Calculator

Calculator for computing restaurant tips and total bill amount.

## Features

- Enter bill amount
- Select tip percentage (5%, 10%, 15%, 20%, 25%)
- Automatic calculation of:
- Tip amount
- Total amount to pay
- Reset all data
- Highlight selected percentage

## What I Learned

- `parseFloat()` - converting string to number
- `isNaN()` - checking for number
- `.toFixed(2)` - rounding to 2 decimal places
- `.classList.add/remove()` - working with CSS classes
- User data validation
- Working with input elements

## How to Run

Simply open `index.html` in your browser.

## How to Use

1. Enter bill amount
2. Select tip percentage
3. Click "=" to calculate
4. Click "Reset" to clear
